# DB exports -- admin_users contains bcrypt hashes for team accounts;
# never push to a public repo. Other exports in /exports/ (site_copy,
# faqs, email_templates, app_config, etc.) are safe.
exports/admin_users_export.json
# Forward-compatible: if you re-run the export AFTER the app has live
